    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >红月<strong>已于2025年6月8日，耗时两年完成重制，现在你可以把它看做一个2025的新游戏！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >红月是一款开放世界ARPG，拥有高度自定义的战斗系统和服装系统，你可以自由组合技能，服装，对服装染色，改变其材质，给技能配置独特的魔法，组合不同配件制作武器等！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras/e1f195c7149785eb4db2ea47d9c8f58b.avif?t=1749554564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras_big/e1f195c7149785eb4db2ea47d9c8f58b.avif?t=1749554564 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras/b347be646726cf038ed984c03a07e39d.avif?t=1749554564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras_big/b347be646726cf038ed984c03a07e39d.avif?t=1749554564 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras/19b063d997a67f38505a63d6f4654018.avif?t=1749554564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras_big/19b063d997a67f38505a63d6f4654018.avif?t=1749554564 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras/114d4b37bbc363c8f09a48e3b0b99997.avif?t=1749554564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras_big/114d4b37bbc363c8f09a48e3b0b99997.avif?t=1749554564 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131820/extras/39f94d0675d0d5e0c83168f25728a8d1.avif?t=1749554564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/21318